{{title 'Actors'}}
<h1>Actors</h1>

<p>It's fun to imagine the game as a TV show with actors playing the various characters.  This is a list of who's playing who.  See <a href="/help/actors">help actors</a> for more information.</p>

<table class="table table-striped">
<thead>
    <th>Actor</th>
    <th>Character</th>
</thead>
<tbody>
{{#each model as |entry|}}
<tr>
    <td>{{entry.actor}}</td>
    <td>{{entry.char_name}}</td>
</tr>
{{/each}}
</tbody>

</table>

{{outlet}}